{"snp2.14:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 2.14 ","snp2.14:0.2":"Dhammikasutta ","snp2.14:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","snp2.14:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava savatthiyam viharati jetavane anathapindikassa arame. ","snp2.14:1.3":"Atha kho dhammiko upasako pancahi upasakasatehi saddhim yena bhagava tenupasankami; upasankamitva bhagavantam abhivadetva ekamantam nisidi. Ekamantam nisinno kho dhammiko upasako bhagavantam gathahi ajjhabhasi: ","snp2.14:2.1":"“Pucchami tam gotama bhuripanna, ","snp2.14:2.2":"Kathankaro savako sadhu hoti; ","snp2.14:2.3":"Yo va agara anagarameti, ","snp2.14:2.4":"Agarino va panupasakase. ","snp2.14:3.1":"Tuvanhi lokassa sadevakassa, ","snp2.14:3.2":"Gatim pajanasi parayananca; ","snp2.14:3.3":"Na catthi tulyo nipunatthadassi, ","snp2.14:3.4":"Tuvanhi buddham pavaram vadanti. ","snp2.14:4.1":"Sabbam tuvam nanamavecca dhammam, ","snp2.14:4.2":"Pakasesi satte anukampamano; ","snp2.14:4.3":"Vivattacchadosi samantacakkhu, ","snp2.14:4.4":"Virocasi vimalo sabbaloke. ","snp2.14:5.1":"Aganchi te santike nagaraja, ","snp2.14:5.2":"Eravano nama jinoti sutva; ","snp2.14:5.3":"Sopi taya mantayitvajjhagama, ","snp2.14:5.4":"Sadhuti sutvana patitarupo. ","snp2.14:6.1":"Rajapi tam vessavano kuvero, ","snp2.14:6.2":"Upeti dhammam paripucchamano; ","snp2.14:6.3":"Tassapi tvam pucchito brusi dhira, ","snp2.14:6.4":"So capi sutvana patitarupo. ","snp2.14:7.1":"Ye kecime titthiya vadasila, ","snp2.14:7.2":"Ajivaka va yadi va nigantha; ","snp2.14:7.3":"Pannaya tam natitaranti sabbe, ","snp2.14:7.4":"Thito vajantam viya sighagamim. ","snp2.14:8.1":"Ye kecime brahmana vadasila, ","snp2.14:8.2":"Vuddha capi brahmana santi keci; ","snp2.14:8.3":"Sabbe tayi atthabaddha bhavanti, ","snp2.14:8.4":"Ye capi anne vadino mannamana. ","snp2.14:9.1":"Ayanhi dhammo nipuno sukho ca, ","snp2.14:9.2":"Yoyam taya bhagava suppavutto; ","snp2.14:9.3":"Tameva sabbepi sussusamana, ","snp2.14:9.4":"Tam no vada pucchito buddhasettha. ","snp2.14:10.1":"Sabbepime bhikkhavo sannisinna, ","snp2.14:10.2":"Upasaka capi tatheva sotum; ","snp2.14:10.3":"Sunantu dhammam vimalenanubuddham, ","snp2.14:10.4":"Subhasitam vasavasseva deva”. ","snp2.14:11.1":"“Sunatha me bhikkhavo savayami vo, ","snp2.14:11.2":"Dhammam dhutam tanca caratha sabbe; ","snp2.14:11.3":"Iriyapatham pabbajitanulomikam, ","snp2.14:11.4":"Sevetha nam atthadaso mutima. ","snp2.14:12.1":"No ve vikale vicareyya bhikkhu, ","snp2.14:12.2":"Game ca pindaya careyya kale; ","snp2.14:12.3":"Akalacarinhi sajanti sanga, ","snp2.14:12.4":"Tasma vikale na caranti buddha. ","snp2.14:13.1":"Rupa ca sadda ca rasa ca gandha, ","snp2.14:13.2":"Phassa ca ye sammadayanti satte; ","snp2.14:13.3":"Etesu dhammesu vineyya chandam, ","snp2.14:13.4":"Kalena so pavise patarasam. ","snp2.14:14.1":"Pindanca bhikkhu samayena laddha, ","snp2.14:14.2":"Eko patikkamma raho niside; ","snp2.14:14.3":"Ajjhattacinti na mano bahiddha, ","snp2.14:14.4":"Niccharaye sangahitattabhavo. ","snp2.14:15.1":"Sacepi so sallape savakena, ","snp2.14:15.2":"Annena va kenaci bhikkhuna va; ","snp2.14:15.3":"Dhammam panitam tamudahareyya, ","snp2.14:15.4":"Na pesunam nopi parupavadam. ","snp2.14:16.1":"Vadanhi eke patiseniyanti, ","snp2.14:16.2":"Na te pasamsama parittapanne; ","snp2.14:16.3":"Tato tato ne pasajanti sanga, ","snp2.14:16.4":"Cittanhi te tattha gamenti dure. ","snp2.14:17.1":"Pindam viharam sayanasananca, ","snp2.14:17.2":"Apanca sanghatirajupavahanam; ","snp2.14:17.3":"Sutvana dhammam sugatena desitam, ","snp2.14:17.4":"Sankhaya seve varapannasavako. ","snp2.14:18.1":"Tasma hi pinde sayanasane ca, ","snp2.14:18.2":"Ape ca sanghatirajupavahane; ","snp2.14:18.3":"Etesu dhammesu anupalitto, ","snp2.14:18.4":"Bhikkhu yatha pokkhare varibindu. ","snp2.14:19.1":"Gahatthavattam pana vo vadami, ","snp2.14:19.2":"Yathakaro savako sadhu hoti; ","snp2.14:19.3":"Na hesa labbha sapariggahena, ","snp2.14:19.4":"Phassetum yo kevalo bhikkhudhammo. ","snp2.14:20.1":"Panam na hane na ca ghatayeyya, ","snp2.14:20.2":"Na canujanna hanatam paresam; ","snp2.14:20.3":"Sabbesu bhutesu nidhaya dandam, ","snp2.14:20.4":"Ye thavara ye ca tasa santi loke. ","snp2.14:21.1":"Tato adinnam parivajjayeyya, ","snp2.14:21.2":"Kinci kvaci savako bujjhamano; ","snp2.14:21.3":"Na haraye haratam nanujanna, ","snp2.14:21.4":"Sabbam adinnam parivajjayeyya. ","snp2.14:22.1":"Abrahmacariyam parivajjayeyya, ","snp2.14:22.2":"Angarakasum jalitamva vinnu; ","snp2.14:22.3":"Asambhunanto pana brahmacariyam, ","snp2.14:22.4":"Parassa daram na atikkameyya. ","snp2.14:23.1":"Sabhaggato va parisaggato va, ","snp2.14:23.2":"Ekassa veko na musa bhaneyya; ","snp2.14:23.3":"Na bhanaye bhanatam nanujanna, ","snp2.14:23.4":"Sabbam abhutam parivajjayeyya. ","snp2.14:24.1":"Majjanca panam na samacareyya, ","snp2.14:24.2":"Dhammam imam rocaye yo gahattho; ","snp2.14:24.3":"Na payaye pivatam nanujanna, ","snp2.14:24.4":"Ummadanantam iti nam viditva. ","snp2.14:25.1":"Mada hi papani karonti bala, ","snp2.14:25.2":"Karenti cannepi jane pamatte; ","snp2.14:25.3":"Etam apunnayatanam vivajjaye, ","snp2.14:25.4":"Ummadanam mohanam balakantam. ","snp2.14:26.1":"Panam na hane na cadinnamadiye, ","snp2.14:26.2":"Musa na bhase na ca majjapo siya; ","snp2.14:26.3":"Abrahmacariya virameyya methuna, ","snp2.14:26.4":"Rattim na bhunjeyya vikalabhojanam. ","snp2.14:27.1":"Malam na dhare na ca gandhamacare, ","snp2.14:27.2":"Mance chamayam va sayetha santhate; ","snp2.14:27.3":"Etanhi atthangikamahuposatham, ","snp2.14:27.4":"Buddhena dukkhantaguna pakasitam. ","snp2.14:28.1":"Tato ca pakkhassupavassuposatham, ","snp2.14:28.2":"Catuddasim pancadasinca atthamim; ","snp2.14:28.3":"Patihariyapakkhanca pasannamanaso, ","snp2.14:28.4":"Atthangupetam susamattarupam. ","snp2.14:29.1":"Tato ca pato upavutthuposatho, ","snp2.14:29.2":"Annena panena ca bhikkhusangham; ","snp2.14:29.3":"Pasannacitto anumodamano, ","snp2.14:29.4":"Yatharaham samvibhajetha vinnu. ","snp2.14:30.1":"Dhammena matapitaro bhareyya, ","snp2.14:30.2":"Payojaye dhammikam so vanijjam; ","snp2.14:30.3":"Etam gihi vattayamappamatto, ","snp2.14:30.4":"Sayampabhe nama upeti deve”ti. ","snp2.14:30.5":"Dhammikasuttam cuddasamam. ","snp2.14:30.6":"Culavaggo dutiyo. ","snp2.14:31.0":"Tassuddanam ","snp2.14:31.1":"Ratanamagandho hiri ca, ","snp2.14:31.2":"mangalam sucilomena; ","snp2.14:31.3":"Dhammacariyanca brahmano, ","snp2.14:31.4":"nava kimsilamutthanam. ","snp2.14:32.1":"Rahulo puna kappo ca, ","snp2.14:32.2":"paribbajaniyam tatha; ","snp2.14:32.3":"Dhammikanca viduno ahu, ","snp2.14:32.4":"culavagganti cuddasati. "}